                                    COMPLEXE HÔTELIER LA BONTÉ - CHB
                                </h1>
                                <div class="small text-muted">
                                    <p class="mb-1">
                                        <strong>RCCM :</strong> RB/ABC/25 B 9901 / <strong>IFU :</strong> 3202577685869
